| `findDuplicates` | O(nÂ˛) | O(n) |
| `calculateRunningBalance` | O(nÂ˛ log n) | O(n log n) |
| `topSpenders` | O(nÂ·u + uÂ˛) | O(n + u log u) |
| `searchTransactions` | O(nÂ˛) | O(n) |
| `processAll` | sum of above | sum of above |

